# Vaulted — Cursor Rules

## What is Vaulted?
Premium home inventory management app for ultra-high-net-worth families in the USA.
Multi-property, multi-user SaaS with strict security requirements.

---

## Current Task: Flutter Mobile App

The NestJS backend is complete (Phases 0-6). Now building the Flutter mobile app.
Rule: **never modify backend files** — only work inside `apps/mobile/`.

---

## Tech Stack (Mobile)

| Package | Version | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| flutter_riverpod | ^2.x | State management |
| go_router | ^13.x | Navigation + auth guard |
| dio | ^5.x | HTTP client |
| flutter_secure_storage | ^9.x | Token storage (Secure Enclave / Keystore) |
| hive_flutter | ^1.x | Offline cache |
| freezed | ^2.x | Immutable data models |
| json_serializable | ^6.x | JSON serialization |
| mobile_scanner | ^5.x | QR code scanning |
| local_auth | ^2.x | Biometric auth |
| cached_network_image | ^3.x | Image caching |
| sentry_flutter | ^8.x | Error monitoring |

